re PR target/18343 (mmix-knuth-mmixware testsuite failure: gcc.dg/builtin-return-1.c)

	PR target/18343
	* gcc.dg/torture/stackalign/builtin-return-1.c (STACK_ARGUMENTS_SIZE):

	(bar): Pass it to __builtin_apply instead of literal 64.
